UCBL Financial and Administrative Manager, Mr Samwel Wado who said the award was awarded to the bank in a short event held in Dar es Salaam. Mr Wado said it was the spirit of his bank to prepare good financial statements which reveal both what the bank is doing and its respective performances. “It is always our spirit to work hard as a financial institution while abiding to transparency, accountability, integrity and ingenuity” he said, adding that in the future such a spirit will continue. NBAA issues awards to various institutions and companies which present the best financial statements which adhere to local and international accounting and auditing standards. These awards are presented annually and the same covered financial statements covering the 2015/16 financial year. In this event giving ceremony institutions and companies which performed better in different categories were presented with respective awards.